HEADWORD: maieutic method
<hw>maieutic method</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A method of teaching by
question and answer; it was used by <persfn>Socrates</persfn> to elicit
truths from his students; -- called also the <altname>Socratic
method</altname></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Maieutics</ent>⟦br⟧
